original_title: 羞恥新入生発育健康診断2020～真夏～
overview: Only 6 girls were selected from my school for the special medical examination conducted by the prefecture. What do you do with a special medical examination? Does it hurt? Is it fun? Would you like to get an injection? We all got on the bus and arrived at a small gymnasium. that? But it doesn't seem to be a school here. There are boys as well as girls ... What will happen to us from now on ...?
title: Shameful Freshmen Developmental Health Examination 2020 ~Midsummer~
